## Vercel

- **Plan:** Vercel Pro. Do not assume Hobby plan or suggest cron limits (e.g. "once per day") as causes for failures.

### Cron authentication

Admin cron routes (`/api/admin/analytics/compute-worker`, `/api/admin/discovery`, `/api/admin/discovery/triage`) bypass auth when `Authorization: Bearer ${CRON_SECRET}` matches. **`CRON_SECRET` must be set in Vercel env vars** (Project Settings → Environment Variables) or cron requests get 401 before the handler runs.
